data.description: This extensively renovated Cape Cod home is ready for its new owner! The interior has been completely transformed with new flooring, updated kitchen cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, a double vanity in the bathroom, and enhanced lighting. Notable design details add a warm and inviting atmosphere to the house, including a charming decorative shiplap fireplace, a practical butcher block island in the kitchen, and the added bonus of extra square footage in a three-season room. The third bedroom offers versatility for expansion or use as an office. Enjoy the comfort of a fenced yard for added privacy, along with convenient alley access. This property is ideally situated near local attractions and within walking distance to the Fairgrounds, making you feel right in the heart of town!
